  "detailed_description": "<h1>CONTENT ROADMAP</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/0a0f71e3bc1b91972b4a8e7ce25f8713.avif?t=1749097895\" width=600 height=1000 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/3125d42584e43a8b8b863d46062eb320.webp?t=1749097895\" width=616 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/785e62b84f4019cb6b3b90f311d1def1.poster.avif?t=1749097895\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/785e62b84f4019cb6b3b90f311d1def1.webm?t=1749097895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/785e62b84f4019cb6b3b90f311d1def1.mp4?t=1749097895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Koboo</strong> draws inspiration from the <strong>difficult</strong> 2D souls-like combat from Dead Cells, the scale of Shadow of the Colossus and the <strong>enchanting world</strong> of Princess Mononoke. <strong>Death is no longer the end!</strong> Strategic builds, skillful positioning and correct timings will get your further in your next run so you can restore balance to the <strong>ancient ecosystem</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/08c2283ae289fe7f298028350c92d919.webp?t=1749097895\" width=616 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/4a7648e8502c814067521440619c4586.poster.avif?t=1749097895\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/4a7648e8502c814067521440619c4586.webm?t=1749097895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/4a7648e8502c814067521440619c4586.mp4?t=1749097895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customize Your Build</strong> - Dual wield weapons that each have their own <strong>4 upgrades paths</strong> to suit your playstyle. Learn Animal Abilities which will powerup through <strong>branching upgrade paths</strong> making you even stronger by the end of your run!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/9e805c5747f3fd134cd1ef14ef26427f.webp?t=1749097895\" width=616 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/306e243769dedae5ab9f01f1873ad48e.poster.avif?t=1749097895\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/306e243769dedae5ab9f01f1873ad48e.webm?t=1749097895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/306e243769dedae5ab9f01f1873ad48e.mp4?t=1749097895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collectables Galore!</strong> - Collect flower seeds, catch bugs, meet fish and befriend the forest animals to unlock Favor. Use Favor in the shop to unlock new <strong>Weapons, Animal Abilities, Infusions, Relics and upgrades</strong> so your future runs will have even more variety!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >More Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Branching Paths</strong> - 7 worlds to explore each with their own enemies and final boss </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Specialize</strong> - Create a unique build by combining Weapon Upgrades, Animal Abilities, Relics and Weapon Infusions </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect</strong> - Go friendly fishing, catch bugs and plant your own garden after boss fights </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Secrets</strong> - Metroidvania inspired exploration to help you discover the secrets of the Ancient Forest... </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Accessibility</strong> - Many accessibility and gameplay options </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Controls</strong> - Full controller support and control rebinding</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/776170b5c78dc05843ac3f46bd8949c5.avif?t=1749097895\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Koboo: The Tree Spirit</strong> wouldn't be possible without the incredible support of our amazing Kickstarter community. Their passion and constructive feedback continue to shape the game, making it even better than we ever dreamed! You can follow our development and talk to us live on <strong>Discord</strong> anytime, we will respond as soon as possible. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Thank you! ❤</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >- Jerome and Simon</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/3125d42584e43a8b8b863d46062eb320.webp?t=1749097895\" width=616 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/785e62b84f4019cb6b3b90f311d1def1.poster.avif?t=1749097895\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/785e62b84f4019cb6b3b90f311d1def1.webm?t=1749097895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/785e62b84f4019cb6b3b90f311d1def1.mp4?t=1749097895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Koboo</strong> draws inspiration from the <strong>difficult</strong> 2D souls-like combat from Dead Cells, the scale of Shadow of the Colossus and the <strong>enchanting world</strong> of Princess Mononoke. <strong>Death is no longer the end!</strong> Strategic builds, skillful positioning and correct timings will get your further in your next run so you can restore balance to the <strong>ancient ecosystem</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/08c2283ae289fe7f298028350c92d919.webp?t=1749097895\" width=616 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/4a7648e8502c814067521440619c4586.poster.avif?t=1749097895\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/4a7648e8502c814067521440619c4586.webm?t=1749097895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/4a7648e8502c814067521440619c4586.mp4?t=1749097895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customize Your Build</strong> - Dual wield weapons that each have their own <strong>4 upgrades paths</strong> to suit your playstyle. Learn Animal Abilities which will powerup through <strong>branching upgrade paths</strong> making you even stronger by the end of your run!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/9e805c5747f3fd134cd1ef14ef26427f.webp?t=1749097895\" width=616 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/306e243769dedae5ab9f01f1873ad48e.poster.avif?t=1749097895\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/306e243769dedae5ab9f01f1873ad48e.webm?t=1749097895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/306e243769dedae5ab9f01f1873ad48e.mp4?t=1749097895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collectables Galore!</strong> - Collect flower seeds, catch bugs, meet fish and befriend the forest animals to unlock Favor. Use Favor in the shop to unlock new <strong>Weapons, Animal Abilities, Infusions, Relics and upgrades</strong> so your future runs will have even more variety!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >More Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Branching Paths</strong> - 7 worlds to explore each with their own enemies and final boss </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Specialize</strong> - Create a unique build by combining Weapon Upgrades, Animal Abilities, Relics and Weapon Infusions </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect</strong> - Go friendly fishing, catch bugs and plant your own garden after boss fights </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Secrets</strong> - Metroidvania inspired exploration to help you discover the secrets of the Ancient Forest... </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Accessibility</strong> - Many accessibility and gameplay options </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Controls</strong> - Full controller support and control rebinding</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/776170b5c78dc05843ac3f46bd8949c5.avif?t=1749097895\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Koboo: The Tree Spirit</strong> wouldn't be possible without the incredible support of our amazing Kickstarter community. Their passion and constructive feedback continue to shape the game, making it even better than we ever dreamed! You can follow our development and talk to us live on <strong>Discord</strong> anytime, we will respond as soon as possible. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Thank you! ❤</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >- Jerome and Simon</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
